{"tid":656399,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝗禍】貓頭鷹一家大細出沒　疑遭電筒照住影市民報警","createTime":"2018-05-07T08:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T22:15:05.000Z","uid":61589,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ab8c98feb41ceead762ce50304ec963d3e1d8a","tid":656399,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:41:18.000Z","msg":"近日一個公園內的一家貓頭鷹儼如明星，出現的白胸鳥亦吸引大批市民及龍友趁墟，引起全城熱潮。雖然保育團體及在場職員再三提醒，雀鳥適宜遠觀，但缺德人士卻繼續懶理。近日網上流傳，有人用丫叉射食物餵雀；有人以強光電筒照射鳥巢；更有人把貓頭鷹放在身上把玩。這些舉動嚴重騷擾貓頭鷹生活，惹來網民狠批自私缺德。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook群組「香港自然生態論壇」上周五（4日）有人張貼照片，發現有人為求拍攝白胸鳥進食照，竟在公園以丫叉「射魚出去俾雀食」，網民直指他藏有攻擊性武器，而所作所為不僅打擾雀鳥生活，亦隨時對牠們造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n而昨日（6日）網上亦流傳圖片，小貓頭鷹停留在一名男子的大髀上，圍觀市民起哄上前拍照，雖然大家樂在其中，但專家指，如意外令幼鳥受傷，或會對其成長產生不良影響。此外，更有指貓頭鷹一家因長期被龍友用電筒照射，現已「搬竇」至另一棵樹上。<br />\n<br />\n有網民慨嘆，現時法例對自私行為未有足夠管制：「幾時有例可以管到呢班人&hellip;&hellip;定有冇計一拍兩散，大家都唔使影&hellip;寧願咁（先救到啲雀）。」<br />\n<br />\n警方今日(7日）早上6時許接獲報案，指有人在該公園內，用電筒照射樹上的貓頭鷹巢穴進行拍攝，惟警員到場調查時，未見有人用電筒拍攝，故向在場人士作出勸喻後離開。根據《野生動物保護條例》，野生雀鳥，包括貓頭鷹及白胸鳥，均屬野生動物受保護，任何人干擾野生雀鳥、鳥巢及鳥蛋均屬違法，定罪最高可被判罰款10萬元及監禁1年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/163738_98162f770ea249c2c7eb13eb87ab737c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F163738_98162f770ea249c2c7eb13eb87ab737c.png&h=121660e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/163759_fcd2af2adb5d472655f8cd9eeaf1f175.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F163759_fcd2af2adb5d472655f8cd9eeaf1f175.png&h=ab928744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/162923_3501dcd1faa4139c7a0cc9d518eae814.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F162923_3501dcd1faa4139c7a0cc9d518eae814.png&h=e968d300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成班港蝗有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD支那基因出哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695fcded4de7c15bfa56a557e760592200fb591e","tid":656399,"uid":48964,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"先天基因相似，後天人口溝淡，而家已經港蝗不分<br />\n<br />\n尤其50-60歲個層"},{"pid":"2f75773789b30f192f8d77261c5266e27e5c37ce","tid":656399,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528b87c7cf1652ebe926fbcb3e1fab990c520be3","tid":656399,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e1b1012937dd7f1075d9176ddc9d4800a98277","tid":656399,"uid":179283,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"咁多相機 唔講以為有恐龍出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前世未見過貓頭鷹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94aab31dfa77626ab8f4d34a12b94ae71014895","tid":656399,"uid":29514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"慈雲山德愛隔離個公園，果然公屋區多垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde9fa08e8e7ed239eac49e0142fb3f47870712f","tid":656399,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"影女係咪都係呢班？"},{"pid":"d78a900582ace3047321868a9d3ecb2a148aaeb4","tid":656399,"